OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,FA special educational needs school in
OL,7,FKent has been nominated as being in
OL,8,Fthe top ten best in the world today.
OL,10,FFive Acre Wood School in Maidstone has
OL,11,Fentered the World's Best School Prize
OL,12,Ffor its innovative learning
OL,13,Fenvironments.
OL,15,FThe school currently has more than 870
OL,16,Fpupils aged 4-19 described as having
OL,17,Fprofound, severe and complex learning
OL,18,Fdifficulties, and more than 500 staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
