PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,FPupils can learn retail and
OL,7,Fhospitality skills in a cafe on site
OL,8,For try their hand at construction.
OL,10,FTeachers want students - who have
OL,11,Fcomplex needs and disabilities - to
OL,12,Fbuild life skills beyond the
OL,13,Fclassroom, to set them up for working
OL,14,Flife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
