FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Headteacher
OL,7,FTim Williams said: "It's an incredible
OL,8,Fhonour, an incredible accolade to be
OL,9,Frecognised alongside some of the most
OL,10,Finspiring schools in the world and I
OL,11,Fthink it puts Five Acre Wood on the
OL,12,Fmap both in the UK in Kent but also
OL,13,Fway beyond.
OL,15,F"We're really clear that this accolade
OL,16,Fis nice, it's lovely to be shortlisted
OL,17,Fbut this is about our pupils, this is
OL,18,Fabout our staff, this is about all the
OL,19,Fpeople that help make Five Acre Wood
OL,20,Fthe very special place it is."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,FFAW has its own hospitality training
OL,7,Facademy in a former first-class train
OL,8,Fcarriage, next door to the coffee
OL,9,Froastery where they brew their own
OL,10,Fbeans, and a shop they can sell them
OL,11,Fin.
OL,13,FThere is also a school radio station
OL,14,Fand global record company to give
OL,15,Fvulnerable children the best chance to
OL,16,Flearn life and employability skills to
OL,17,F"achieve new possibles."
OL,19,FThere's even a library located in an
OL,20,FAirbus A319 airplane within the school
OL,21,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
