OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,FHelen Grant OBE, MP for Maidstone and
OL,7,FMalling, said: "I am absolutely
OL,8,Fdelighted to congratulate everyone at
OL,9,FFive Acre Wood School - pupils, staff,
OL,10,Ffamilies and the leadership team - on
OL,11,Fbeing shortlisted in the Top 10 for
OL,12,Fthe World School Prize for Innovation
OL,13,F2026.
OL,15,F"This is a remarkable achievement and
OL,16,Fa testament to the school's
OL,17,Fcreativity, ambition and unwavering
OL,18,Fcommitment to providing exceptional
OL,19,Fopportunities for its pupils.
OL,26,@oD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,F"Having visited the school and seen
OL,7,Fits pioneering approach first-hand, I
OL,8,Fknow just how special Five Acre Wood
OL,9,Fis.
OL,11,F"From the FAWrient Express and
OL,12,FPlatform FAW to its unique learning
OL,13,Fenvironments, the school continually
OL,14,Ffinds innovative ways to inspire and
OL,15,Fempower young people.
OL,17,F"Five Acre Wood is not only one of the
OL,18,Flargest special schools in the
OL,19,Fcountry, but one of the very best.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,F"This international recognition is
OL,7,Frichly deserved. Every pupil should be
OL,8,Fincredibly proud of their contribution
OL,9,Fto this success, and I wish the whole
OL,10,Fschool community the very best of luck
OL,11,Fin the next stage of the competition."
OL,13,FVikas Pota, Founder of T4 Education
OL,14,Fand the World's Best School Prizes,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Congratulations to Five Acre
OL,16,FWood School on being shortlisted for
OL,17,Fthe fifth annual World's Best School
OL,18,FPrizes.
OL,26,@sD@fO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
