OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782429507
OL,3,CInside the UK's largest SEN School
OL,4,Cnominated as one of the world's best
OL,6,F"It has shown that Maidstone's schools
OL,7,Ftruly stand among the best in the
OL,8,Fworld.
OL,10,F"Each one of these exemplary schools
OL,11,Fshortlisted for this global schools
OL,12,Fprize has, in its own unique way,
OL,13,Fhelped prepare young people for a
OL,14,Fworld that has never seemed so
OL,15,Funcertain.
OL,17,F"It is more important than ever that
OL,18,Four schools grow the leaders we'll
OL,19,Fneed to face massive challenges from
OL,20,Frising conflict and inequality to
OL,21,Fpopulism and climate breakdown.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
